    <title>Min. RPM Limit 8-2, Semi Auto Downshift</title>
    <description>to 2nd:  Gear 3-2&#013;&#010;to 3st:   Gear 8-3&#013;&#010;Value 0 allows upshifts when the car speed = 0 km/h&#013;&#010;Value 1 allows upshifts when the car speed &gt; 0 km/h&#013;&#010;but don&apos;t make downshift&#013;&#010;Minimum turbine RPM below which the TCU will perform semi automatic &#010;downshift</description>
